Hey guys, I've been hunting strawberry for a while now, and I kept running into the C-rank mission they said he was at, but never got him. I thought it was just my horrible luck, until I played this mission.

You got a Ninja Ally - Strawberry!
An orange-haired, lanky guy standing around shrugs. "They were going to make ME do that. Thanks!"
(+2 Taijutsu Levels, +6 on Reaper Missions!)

might wanna update your wiki record ^^

Otherwise, great site.
